  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A wild elephant rammed motorcycles lined up near a petrol station",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "An incident has been reported where a wild elephant rammed the motorcycles lined up to fill up with petrol.",
        "From the evening of Thursday 28th, motor vehicles were parked one after the other in order to fill up with petrol at the petrol filling station located in Vellaveli under the Batticaloa, Porativu tax area.",
        "In this case, on the night of Thursday 29th, a wild elephant came to the area and showed its strength on the motorcycles that were lined up, according to the local people.",
        "The said wild elephant passed through the village of Punnakulam in the area and came to the area where the Vellaveli filling station is located.",
        "In this case, 7 motorcycles were damaged due to vandalism of the motorcycles placed in the queue.",
        "According to the Village Service Officer of the area, 3 motorcycles were completely damaged and the other 4 motorcycles were partially damaged. According to the people of the area, around 30 lakhs of rupees have been lost due to this.",
        "We are suffering a lot because we do not have money to send our children to school and for agricultural activities. In this case, we kept our motorcycles only to fill up with petrol.",
        "This will affect the education and livelihood of our children. It is like stepping on a fallen tree. The victims expressed concern that the government should help us."
      ],
